ParallelChunk.en:
We do not want to support any new protectionism - absolutely not; 
          rather
        , we want the seven core Labour Standards of the International Labour Organisation to also be guaranteed for workers in the ACP and developing countries.

We request that the Community method as per Article 48 be used; we expect a concrete proposal from the Commission which will form the basis for the negotiations; 
          and
         we also expect to reach a consensus with the Council and the Commission concerning the agenda and the procedure for the next Intergovernmental Conference.
